1 A SENATE RESOLUTION CONFIRMING LESLIE COOLEY DISMUKES AS SECRETARY
2 OF THE DEPARTMENT OF ADULT CORRECTION.
3 Be it resolved by the Senate:
4 SECTION 1. Having given due consideration to the matter, the Senate confirms
5 Leslie Cooley Dismukes as Secretary of the Department of Adult Correction.
6 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon adoption.
